## Run auth.http → Login first to populate {{token}}

### Dwarf Warrior — tanky melee bruiser (27 pts)
POST {{host}}/characters
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Thorin Ironfist",
  "raceId": "dwarf",
  "classId": "warrior",
  "strength": 15,
  "dexterity": 8,
  "constitution": 15,
  "intelligence": 8,
  "wisdom": 10,
  "charisma": 10
}

